{"tid":2215340,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Rocket League Free-to-play 正式喺Epic Store推出！！","createTime":"2020-09-24T02:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T11:55:51.000Z","uid":370779,"like":1,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"94be1999063a91fed78a5696275bfb6432478c21","tid":2215340,"uid":370779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQ6GiQm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQ6GiQm.png&h=416928b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/rocketleague/status/1308789263127908352?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frocketleague%2Fstatus%2F1308789263127908352%3Fs%3D21&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=b247e3c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frocketleague%2Fstatus%2F1308789263127908352%3Fs%3D21&h=02c64b4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/rocketleague/status/1308789263127908352?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n發覺香港（至少喺連登）冇乜人討論Rocket League<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我自己本身喺2017年開始玩，play time有成差唔多1600hours，呢隻game可以話係我玩過最好玩嘅game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果你係一個casual gamer，你可以玩casual playlist；如果你想competitive啲嘅，你可以玩rank；想同frd玩又可以create個private match<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以我好希望趁住f2p推出可以有多啲香港人試吓玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係一啲gameplay俾大家睇吓RL係咩嚟嘅<br />\n<br />\nRocket League Championship Series - Final (Highlights) Cloud9 vs Dignitas<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/geazzwAxWxg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgeazzwAxWxg&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=e2cb0248\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/geazzwAxWxg</a><br />\n<br />\n2v2 gameplay <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CzJu9BKZe2A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCzJu9BKZe2A&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=4f3bc34a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CzJu9BKZe2A</a>"},{"pid":"b834d42d7aa799d74a2ec484a5be8986f7019834","tid":2215340,"uid":370779,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:37:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家有咩問題可以隨便問我"},{"pid":"d5c8a00b0a7bfb5b69aed37d39fc3a78345170c8","tid":2215340,"uid":370779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:38:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e59624f3a0c36f78bdeca99f63e15109aebfcb1","tid":2215340,"uid":350540,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:40:31.000Z","msg":"epic不了"},{"pid":"133f148c20eee5d956137aa0f7c0581a2de0ecfc","tid":2215340,"uid":79793,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:41:08.000Z","msg":"epic不了"},{"pid":"2c389b4cbd38191c95f3b022377d20135e4a78d1","tid":2215340,"uid":222168,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"正垃圾 epic都推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4a352de1494f8d592ad517a5553e1ee69d4125","tid":2215340,"uid":78819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:47:32.000Z","msg":"到依家都仲有玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />空中波好廢"},{"pid":"1a303b6af73525c07dd5a5af03be8881849f7ed8","tid":2215340,"uid":2192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:52:29.000Z","msg":"我之前都有玩，仲水左個朋友，佢玩到沉迷，但都係得兩個人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f800952c09543d7b6bfca7d29fd8735422469995","tid":2